---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';

const jsonLd = {
  '@context': 'https://schema.org',
  '@type': 'WebPage',
  name: 'Privacy Policy — CSIORS',
  description: 'How CSIORS handles personal data, respondent anonymity, and GDPR compliance.',
  url: 'https://csiors.org/privacy/',
  isPartOf: { '@type': 'WebSite', name: 'CSIORS', url: 'https://csiors.org' },
};
---
<BaseLayout
  lang="en"
  title="Privacy Policy — CSIORS"
  description="How CSIORS handles personal data, respondent anonymity, and GDPR compliance as a Slovakia-registered research institute."
  jsonLd={jsonLd}
>
<div class="container">

  <section class="page-hero">
    <div class="page-hero-tag">Legal</div>
    <h1 class="page-hero-title">Privacy Policy</h1>
    <p class="page-hero-lede">The Czech-Slovak Institute of Oriental Studies (CSIORS) is committed to protecting the privacy of its website visitors, newsletter subscribers, and field survey respondents. This policy explains how we collect, use, and safeguard personal data.</p>
  </section>

  <section class="page-section">
    <div class="about-rule"></div>
    <h2 class="section-heading">Data controller</h2>
    <p>CSIORS is a research institute registered in the Slovak Republic. For questions regarding this policy or your personal data, contact us at <a href="mailto:info@csiors.org">info@csiors.org</a>.</p>
  </section>

  <section class="page-section">
    <div class="about-rule"></div>
    <h2 class="section-heading">What data we collect</h2>
    <p><strong>Website visitors:</strong> We use privacy-respecting analytics that do not track individual users. No cookies are placed for analytics purposes. Standard server logs (IP address, browser type, pages visited) may be retained temporarily by our hosting provider, Vercel.</p>
    <p><strong>Newsletter subscribers:</strong> When you subscribe to our newsletter, we collect your email address. This is processed through Buttondown, our newsletter platform. You can unsubscribe at any time using the link in every email.</p>
    <p><strong>Field survey respondents:</strong> Our anonymous field survey, hosted on KoboToolbox, is designed to collect no personally identifiable information. Responses are transmitted over encrypted connections and stored on EU-based servers (eu.kobotoolbox.org). Participation is entirely voluntary.</p>
    <p><strong>Contact form:</strong> If you contact us through our website, your name and email are used solely to respond to your inquiry.</p>
  </section>

  <section class="page-section">
    <div class="about-rule"></div>
    <h2 class="section-heading">How we use your data</h2>
    <p>We use personal data exclusively for the purpose for which it was provided: delivering newsletters to subscribers, responding to inquiries, and conducting research analysis from anonymized field data. We do not sell, rent, or share personal data with third parties for marketing purposes.</p>
  </section>

  <section class="page-section">
    <div class="about-rule"></div>
    <h2 class="section-heading">Respondent anonymity</h2>
    <p>Protecting field respondents is our highest priority. Survey responses are anonymized at the point of collection. No names, GPS coordinates, or device identifiers are recorded. Published analysis uses aggregated data only — individual responses are never disclosed. For full details, see our <a href="/methodology">Data Methodology</a> page.</p>
  </section>

  <section class="page-section">
    <div class="about-rule"></div>
    <h2 class="section-heading">Your rights under GDPR</h2>
    <p>As a Slovakia-registered entity, CSIORS operates under the EU General Data Protection Regulation (GDPR). You have the right to access, correct, or delete your personal data; withdraw consent at any time; request data portability; and lodge a complaint with the Slovak Data Protection Authority (Úrad na ochranu osobných údajov SR).</p>
    <p>To exercise any of these rights, email <a href="mailto:info@csiors.org">info@csiors.org</a>.</p>
  </section>

  <section class="page-section">
    <div class="about-rule"></div>
    <h2 class="section-heading">Third-party services</h2>
    <p>We use the following services that may process data on our behalf: Vercel (hosting), Buttondown (newsletter), KoboToolbox (field surveys), and GitHub (source code). Each operates under their own privacy policies and applicable data protection agreements.</p>
  </section>

  <section class="page-section">
    <div class="about-rule"></div>
    <h2 class="section-heading">Changes to this policy</h2>
    <p>We may update this policy to reflect changes in our practices or legal requirements. Material changes will be noted on this page. This policy was last updated on March 26, 2026.</p>
  </section>

</div>
</BaseLayout>
